animeTitle: UFO Princess Valkyrie 2: Juunigatsu no Yasoukyoku (Dub)
otherNames: UFO Ultramaiden Valkyrie 2: December Nocturne; UFO Princess Valkyrie - December's Nocturne; UFO Princess Walküre 2; 円盤皇女ワるきゅーレ 十二月の夜想曲
synopsis: Valkyrie, Kazuto, Akina, Hydra and friends are back for more when the Key of time suddenly appears along with many other mysterious happenings. All seemed to be linked to a person named `Valkyrie Ghost` who`s only goal is stealing Kazuto for herself. As they team up against this seeming unbeatable foe they dig deeper into the mysterious past of Valkyrie`s home planet, Valhalla.
